### ✅ Shell (keep simple)

* [x] bash default
* [x] optional `zsh` + `starship`

### ✅ Tools

* [x] `fastfetch`
* [x] `btop`
* [x] `git`
* [x] `base-devel`

### ✅ Modern CLI

* [x] `eza`
* [x] `bat`
* [x] `ripgrep`
* [x] `fzf`
* [x] `zoxide`

### ✅ Kernel hacking (Kitest focus)

* [x] `linux-headers`, `perf`, `gdb`, `strace`, `bc`, `bison`, `flex`, `sparse`, `pahole` (Arch: `pahole` replaces old `dwarves` pkg name)

---

# 📦 9. APP ECOSYSTEM

### ✅ Flatpak

* [x] `flatpak`
* [x] Flathub enabled
* [x] **Brave** + **Steam** + **Flatseal** via Flathub (`kitest-desktop-extras.sh`); default HTTP(S) handler → Brave when install succeeds; no native `steam` / **multilib**

### ✅ Desktop / office / games (profile)

* [x] **LibreOffice** (`libreoffice-fresh`)
* [x] **Steam** (Flatpak `com.valvesoftware.Steam`)
* [x] **oneko** — Flatpak `com.daidouji.oneko` + autostart `flatpak run …` (native `oneko` removed from Arch repos)

👉 Goal:

* apps installable without breaking base system

---

# 🧪 10. LIVE ENVIRONMENT QUALITY

### ✅ Must work in **QEMU**

* [ ] boots without errors — **validate** after ISO build (`./qemu-smoke.sh …`)
* [ ] network works
* [ ] KDE loads
* [ ] theme applied

### ✅ No blocking bugs

* [ ] no service failures
* [ ] no missing firmware

### ✅ Build host notes

* [x] **Docker:** `pacstrap` needs **`--privileged`** (or equivalent caps); see [README.md](README.md).
* [x] **GitHub Actions:** `build-archiso.yml` uses `container.options: --privileged`.

---

# 🧠 11. CUSTOMIZATION ENGINE (future-proofing)

### ✅ `customize_airootfs.sh`

* [x] user creation
* [x] services enable
* [x] theme setup (skel + `xdg-user-dirs-update`)
* [x] aliases
* [x] flatpak setup

👉 This script = **core of your distro**

